Happy 4th Birthday, my magical girl Arika! ❤️🎉

How did four years pass in the blink of an eye? From your tiny cries to becoming the little chatterbox who fills our home with laughter and endless questions—you’ve made every moment magical.❤️
I love you beyond words can ever express, you are my greatest blessing.🥹❤️🥹

You complete me in ways I never knew were possible. Your hugs heal, your giggles light up my world, and your little dreams fill my heart with endless hope. Watching you grow is the most beautiful journey of my life. 💕

May you always shine as brightly as you do today, my love. Keep spreading your magic wherever you go my little star! ✨😘❤️🥰🤗🌸

#happybirthdayarika #myheartinhumanform #mydaughterismyworld #mywholeheart #fouryearsofpurelove #blessedbeyondwords #motherdaughterlove #motherdaughterbond #mummalovesyou❤️💕😍😘

Happy 10th, My Love!!❤️

Ten years—what a journey it has been! We’ve had our share of beautiful moments, but we’ve also walked through fire, facing challenges that tested us in ways we never imagined. The road wasn’t just bumpy; at times, it felt impossible to walk. I hit some of the lowest points of my life during this journey, questioning everything, struggling to hold on. But through it all, we made it.

Through every tear, every heartbreak, and every storm, we found a way back to each other. We didn’t just survive; we grew, we evolved, and we built something unshakable. And today, as we stand together, stronger than ever, I’m grateful for every battle we fought because it led us here—to a love that is real, raw, and unbreakable.

Here’s to us, to everything we’ve endured, and to the love that never gave up. Love you always!

#10YearsOfUs #StrongerThroughTheStorm #foreverandalways
